comment: /**  * Containers and tests are enabled if {@code @EnabledIf} is present on the  * corresponding test class or test method and the configured expression  * evaluates to {@code true}.  */
code: /**  * Containers and tests are enabled if {@code @EnabledIf} is present on the  * corresponding test class or test method and the configured expression  * evaluates to {@code true}.  */ @Override public ConditionEvaluationResult evaluateExecutionCondition(ExtensionContext context) {     return evaluateAnnotation(EnabledIf.class, EnabledIf::expression, EnabledIf::reason, EnabledIf::loadContext, true, context). }
